# 16 - Fitness Program Designer
# Create personalized workout plans

NAME fitness-designer
INPUT fitness_goal
INPUT current_fitness DEFAULT "sedentary"
INPUT equipment DEFAULT "minimal home equipment"
INPUT days_per_week DEFAULT 4

GOAL assess "Scope: $fitness_goal from $current_fitness with $equipment, $days_per_week days/week. Brief assessment."
GOAL design "Design program: 4-6 exercises per day, sets/reps. Simple progression (add weight or reps)."
GOAL schedule "Create $days_per_week-day schedule. One line per day."
GOAL guide "Add 2-3 form tips for key lifts. Skip nutrition unless asked. Save to fitness-program-output.md."

RUN create USING assess, design, schedule, guide
